let the cat out of the bag.data-term: let the cat out of the bag

examples.en: She wore a very revealing shirt.
That skirt is much too revealing.
The article shaded the truth by revealing only one side of the story.
The book is a revealing account of being part of a gang.
He may be prosecuted for revealing secrets about the security agency.
Her dress was scanty and revealing.
Investigative reporters uncloaked the real estate tycoon, revealing him to be nothing more than a slumlord.
